 <text id="F3036T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus reports on the death of a relative in battle and expresses concern that his wife is
     having to work so hard at home.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-03-24">March the 24th 1864</date>
      <name type="place"><orig reg="Jacksonville">Jackson vill</orig> florady<lb/><orig
       reg="Headquarters">Headquaters</orig>
       <unclear>Tenalam</unclear></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute/>
    </opener>

    <p>i take this Present time to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> you <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines to let you <orig reg="know">now</orig> that i am Well at
     present and i hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig>
     <orig reg="these">thes</orig>
     <orig reg="few">fu</orig> lines reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you in the same state of <orig reg="health">healte</orig> i <orig
      reg="receive">recve</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig>
     <orig reg="kind">kinde</orig> letter and i Was <orig reg="very">verry</orig> glad to hear <orig
      reg="from">frum</orig> you and all the rest i am sorry to think how you <orig reg="have"
     >hafe</orig> to get <orig reg="along">a long</orig> i never <orig reg="thought">thot</orig>
     that you <orig reg="Would">Wod</orig>
     <orig reg="have">hafte</orig> to <orig reg="Work">Wark</orig> so hard to get <orig reg="along"
      >a long</orig> but i <orig reg="think">thin</orig> that i Will be <orig reg="home">hom</orig>
     <orig reg="before">befor</orig> long <orig reg="for">fer</orig>
     <orig reg="they">tha</orig> Will <orig reg="have">hafte</orig> to pay us <orig reg="again">a
      gane</orig> the 22 of day of march i <orig reg="have">hafe</orig> not got <orig reg="time"
     >tim</orig> to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> much but i am happy to say that We had a hard
     fight but We all got out safe but William <orig reg="Christy">Cristy</orig> he Was <orig
      reg="killed">kild</orig> on the <orig reg="ground">grond</orig> and Joe Was <orig
      reg="Wounded">Wonded</orig> i the head but he has <orig reg="Come">Com</orig> back to the
      <orig reg="regiment">redgmete</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gan</orig> and is <orig reg="getting">geting</orig>
     <orig reg="along">a long</orig> very Well and the boy all <orig reg="have">haf</orig> good
      <orig reg="health">healte</orig> so far you must <orig reg="excuse">excus</orig> this <orig
      reg="short">sorte</orig> letter <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <orig reg="have">hafe</orig> not
     got <orig reg="time">tim</orig> to <orig reg="write">rite</orig> much but i <unclear>shule</unclear>
     <orig reg="write">rit</orig>
     <orig reg="soon">son</orig>
     <orig reg="again">a gan</orig> and <orig reg="then">than</orig> i Will tell you all <orig
      reg="about">a bout</orig> the <unclear>tims</unclear>
     <orig reg="please">pleas</orig>
     <orig reg="write">rite</orig>
     <orig reg="soon">son</orig> and let me <orig reg="know">now</orig>
     <orig reg="Where">Whear</orig> John is going to in the spring <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> you
      <orig reg="write">rit</orig> Direct you letter to Hilton Head South <orig reg="Carolina"
      >Carlina</orig> Co K 54 <abbr expan="Massachusetts">Mss</abbr>
     <orig reg="volunteers">volintears</orig> nothing <orig reg="more">mor</orig> at present but
     still <orig reg="remain">rima</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David Demus</signed>
     <seg type="postscript">to Marry Demus</seg>
    </closer>
   </div1>
